Title: Barter Up
Description:
Greetings, friend

I've  heard you've come across something that I would be interested in. 

A very strong-smelling morsel, I'd like to see it. 

You know, just to see if it's worth my time. 

Your extremely nice friend, 

Ponzo
ObjectivesText: Bring the Pungent Morsel to Ponzo in Loamm.
